text: The Jönköping Theatre () is a theatre in the town of Jönköping in Sweden. It has seating capacity of 356 and is also used for concerts. It was opened on 2 December 1904. ==References== ==Other websites== *Programbolaget Category:1904 establishments in Sweden Category:Buildings and structures in Sweden Category:Buildings and structures in Jönköping Category:Theatres
title: Jönköping Theatre
